<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
 <head>
  <title>CSS Test: font-size</title>
  <meta name="flags" content="ahem" />
  <link rel="help" href="http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-CSS1#font-size"/>
  <link rel="author" title="CSS1 Test Suite Contributors" href="http://www.w3.org/Style/CSS/Test/CSS1/current/tsack.html"/>
  <link rel="author" title="Ian Hickson" href="mailto:ian@hixie.ch"/>
  <style type="text/css"><![CDATA[
   div { color: navy; font: 1em/1 Ahem; margin: 0 2em; }
   .a {font-size: 0.5in;}
   .b {font-size: 1.27cm;}
   .c {font-size: 12.7mm;}
   .d {font-size: 36pt;}
   .e {font-size: 3pc;}
   .h {font-size: 48px;}
  ]]></style>
 </head>
 <body>
  <p>There should be a solid single uninterrupted smooth column of blue below.</p>
  <div class="a"> x </div>
  <div class="b"> x </div>
  <div class="c"> x </div>
  <div class="d"> x </div>
  <div class="e"> x </div>
  <div class="h"> x </div>
 </body>
</html>
